      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL IT MISTER (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 4 last run (19.97) at this track. Has good early burn and is suited drawn on the inside. Likely to be in the finish again. BELLA MAPLE (2) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten one length, (20.00) at this track. Speedy beginner who should be prominent early on from an inside box. Well placed and gets her chance. ON THE STRIP (8) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at Murray Bridge Straight following on from a win (20.03) at this track the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Leading chance. SEBON DIVA (7) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
